BRAND VOICE
Character: A smart friend who happens to understand money. Honest, clear, calm. 
Voice Element Rule Tone Trustworthy, modern, approachable. Never condescending. SL Short and clear. Plain EA. Punctuation Normal. Light use of em dashes for rhythm. Vocabulary (use) simple, smart, yours, earn, grow, track, clear, control Vocabulary (never) complicated, risky, complex, confusing, overwhelming, don't worry RA "you" and "your money" — personal, direct Never sounds like a bank, a finance professor, a sales pitch 
