NOTES FOR SPECIFIC AGENTS
Lena: Plain EA. No financial jargon. Approachable but smart. Short paragraphs. 
Sofia: LinkedIn is primary for Hourbour (professional + fintech audience). Instagram for lifestyle/visual. Content should feel helpful, not salesy. 
Rio: LinkedIn Ads for professional targeting. Interest targeting: personal finance, budgeting, fintech. Exclude high-net-worth investors (not the target). 
Atlas: Clean, modern visuals. Light or dark theme. App UI screenshots preferred. Data visualization elements welcome (charts, progress bars). 
Kai: SaaS metrics. Watch for churn signals in GA4 (drop in session frequency per user). Flag MRR anomalies 10% MoM. 
Felix: SaaS model. LTV:CAC must stay above 3:1. Monitor MRR, expansion MRR, and contraction MRR separately. 